ass=\"text-lg\" style=\"opacity: 1; transform: none;\"><astro-slot>Our terms and conditions governing the use of our services and website.</astro-slot></p></astro-island> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"section\"> <div class=\"container\"> <div class=\"content\"> <h4 id=\"acceptance-of-terms\">Acceptance of Terms</h4>\n<p>By accessing and using NeonSpark’s website and services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. These terms apply to all visitors, users, and others who access or use our services. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must not use our website or services.</p>\n<p>These Terms and Conditions constitute a legally binding agreement between you and NeonSpark. We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time, and your continued use of our services following any changes indicates your acceptance of the new terms.</p>\n<h4 id=\"use-of-services\">Use of Services</h4>\n<p>NeonSpark provides web design, development, and digital marketing services. Our services are intended for legitimate business purposes and personal use in accordance with these terms. You agree to use our services responsibly and in compliance with all applicable laws and regulations.</p>\n<p><strong>Permitted Uses:</strong> Creating websites, web applications, and digital solutions for your business or personal projects, accessing our portfolio and case studies, contacting us for service inquiries, and downloading resources we make publicly available.</p>\n<p><strong>Prohibited Uses:</strong> Using our services for any illegal or unauthorized purpose, attempting to gain unauthorized access to our systems or networks, distributing malware or harmful code, violating intellectual property rights, or engaging in any activity that could harm our reputation or business operations.</p>\n<p>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of any account information and passwords associated with your use of our services.</p>\n<h4 id=\"intellectual-property-rights\">Intellectual Property Rights</h4>\n<p>All content, materials, and intellectual property on our website and in our services are owned by NeonSpark or our licensors and are protected by copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws. This includes but is not limited to:</p>\n<p><strong>Website Content:</strong> Text, graphics, logos, images, videos, code, and design elements on our website and in our work products.</p>\n<p><strong>Service Deliverables:</strong> Custom designs, code, and solutions created specifically for clients become the property of the client upon full payment, unless otherwise specified in a separate agreement.</p>\n<p><strong>NeonSpark Branding:</strong> Our company name, logo, and branding elements remain our exclusive property and may not be used without written permission.</p>\n<p>You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, or create derivative works from our content without express written consent, except where specifically permitted by law or these terms.</p>\n<h4 id=\"service-terms-and-client-obligations\">Service Terms and Client Obligations</h4>\n<p>When engaging our services, clients agree to provide accurate and complete information necessary for project completion. This includes timely provision of content, feedback, and approvals as outlined in project agreements.</p>\n<p><strong>Project Timelines:</strong> Delivery schedules depend on client cooperation and timely feedback. Delays caused by client factors may result in adjusted timelines and potential additional costs.</p>\n<p><strong>Content Responsibility:</strong> Clients are responsible for ensuring all provided content is original, properly licensed, or used with permission. Clients indemnify NeonSpark against any claims arising from content provided by the client.</p>\n<p><strong>Payment Terms:</strong> Payment schedules and terms are specified in individual project agreements. Late payments may result in project delays or suspension of services.</p>\n<p><strong>Revisions and Changes:</strong> Project scope changes may incur additional costs and timeline adjustments as outlined in project agreements.</p>\n<h4 id=\"limitation-of-liability-and-disclaimers\">Limitation of Liability and Disclaimers</h4>\n<p>Our services are provided “as is” without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. While we strive for excellence in all our work, we cannot guarantee uninterrupted or error-free service.</p>\n<p><strong>Service Availability:</strong> We make reasonable efforts to ensure our website and services are available, but do not guarantee continuous access or freedom from technical issues.</p>\n<p><strong>Third-Party Services:</strong> We are not responsible for the performance or availability of third-party services, hosting providers, or external integrations beyond our control.</p>\n<p><strong>Limitation of Damages:</strong> In no event shall NeonSpark be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services. Our total liability for any claims shall not exceed the amount paid for the specific services in question.</p>\n<p><strong>Professional Advice:</strong> Our services do not constitute legal, financial, or professional advice. Clients should consult appropriate professionals for such matters.</p>\n<p>We encourage clients to review all deliverables promptly and communicate any concerns within reasonable timeframes to ensure satisfactory project outcomes.</p> </div> </div> </section>  </main> <footer> <div class=\"bg-dark backdrop-blur-2xl pb-10\"> <div class=\"container\"> <div class=\"pt-30 pb-20\"> <div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-12 gap-8\"> <div class=\"sm:col-span-6 lg:col-span-3\"> <a href=\"/\" class=\"navbar-brand inline-block\">  <img src=\"/assets/pages/terms-and-condition/logo.BFFbahU8_Z1WHULm.webp\" alt=\"Neonspark\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"height:27px;width:150px\" widt